  <brief_title>Helicobacter Pylori Treatment in Immune Thrombocytopenic Purpura (ITP) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Helicobacter Pylori Infection and Chronic Immune Thrombocytopenic Purpura in Children and Adolescents - A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
