    <measure>platelet response</measure>
    <time_frame>1 year</time_frame>
    <description>Responders: Complete Response (CR), persistent elevation of platelet count to &gt;150×109/L; Partial Response (PR), elevation between 20 and 30×109/L above the baseline values, but between 50 and 149×109/L; No Responders: any of the above categories.</description>
